The '''Northern Plains Resource Council''' is an environmental lobbying organization based in [[Montana]]. It was founded in 1972 to lobby for stricter environmental controls on coal mining and [[coal-fired power plants]].<ref name = history>[http://www.northernplains.org/about/history/ History of Northern Plains Resource Council]</ref>
